#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:172
msgid ""
"**LMCache server** ``--chunk-size`` **= N** (or any multiple of ``N``). "
"This is the rule the connector enforces: LMCache's chunk size must be a "
"multiple of vLLM's unified block size, or registration fails::"
msgstr ""
"**LMCache 服务器** ``--chunk-size`` **= N**（或任何 ``N`` "
"的倍数）。这是连接器强制执行的规则：LMCache 的块大小必须是 vLLM 的统一块大小的倍数，否则注册将失败::"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:178
msgid ""
"**vLLM** ``--max-num-batched-tokens`` **in [N, 2·N)** — setting it equal "
"to ``N`` is the simple, always-valid choice. Outside this range LMCache "
"raises at engine startup. ``align`` mode snapshots the Mamba state only "
"at the *end* of each scheduler step, so each prefill step must advance "
"exactly one block; a larger budget would let a step skip block "
"boundaries, leaving no snapshot for LMCache to store at those prefixes."
msgstr ""
"**vLLM** ``--max-num-batched-tokens`` **在 [N, 2·N)** — 将其设置为 ``N`` "
"是简单且始终有效的选择。在此范围之外，LMCache 在引擎启动时会引发错误。``align`` 模式仅在每个调度器步骤的 *结束* 时快照 "
"Mamba 状态，因此每个预取步骤必须精确推进一个块；更大的预算将允许步骤跳过块边界，从而在这些前缀处没有快照可供 LMCache 存储。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:185
msgid ""
"**vLLM** ``--mamba-cache-mode align --enable-prefix-caching`` — ``align``"
" is mandatory (GDN backends do not support the ``all`` mode)::"
msgstr ""
"**vLLM** ``--mamba-cache-mode align --enable-prefix-caching`` — ``align``"
" 是强制性的（GDN 后端不支持 ``all`` 模式）：:"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:194
msgid ""
"So for a freshly-probed model the whole derivation is just: read ``N`` "
"(step 1), then pass ``--chunk-size N`` to the server and ``--max-num-"
"batched-tokens N`` to vLLM."
msgstr ""
"因此，对于一个新探测的模型，整个推导过程就是：读取 ``N``（步骤 1），然后将 ``--chunk-size N`` 传递给服务器，并将 "
"``--max-num-batched-tokens N`` 传递给 vLLM。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:198
msgid ""
"No ``--no-disable-hybrid-kv-cache-manager`` or attention-backend flag is "
"needed; ``LMCacheMPConnector`` advertises hybrid support and vLLM auto-"
"selects the GDN backend."
msgstr ""
"不需要 ``--no-disable-hybrid-kv-cache-manager`` 或 attention-backend "
"标志；``LMCacheMPConnector`` 宣布支持混合，并且 vLLM 自动选择 GDN 后端。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:203
msgid "Caveats"
msgstr "注意事项"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:205
msgid ""
"Generation is **not bit-exact** between a cached and a fresh run: GDN "
"backends do not support vLLM's batch-invariant mode. Validate with a "
"**score-level** comparison (see `Verifying Correctness`_), not a token-"
"level diff."
msgstr ""
"生成在缓存和新运行之间**不是位精确**的：GDN 后端不支持 vLLM 的批量不变模式。请使用**分数级**比较进行验证（参见 "
"`验证正确性`_），而不是令牌级差异。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:209
msgid ""
"The cached pages are **byte-opaque**, so content-aware features (CacheGen"
" compression, CacheBlend) do not apply, and cache entries must not be "
"shared across engines with different attention backends or kernel block "
"sizes."
msgstr ""
"缓存页面是 **字节不透明** 的，因此内容感知特性（CacheGen "
"压缩、CacheBlend）不适用，并且缓存条目不得在具有不同注意力后端或内核块大小的引擎之间共享。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:212
msgid ""
"Several of these models are **vision-language** (they load a vision "
"tower). The validated, supported path is **text** KV caching; image/video"
" KV caching is not validated."
msgstr ""
"这些模型中的几个是 **视觉-语言** 模型（它们加载一个视觉塔）。经过验证的支持路径是 **文本** KV 缓存；图像/视频 KV "
"缓存尚未经过验证。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:215
msgid ""
"vLLM's Mamba prefix caching in ``align`` mode is marked experimental "
"upstream."
msgstr "vLLM 的 Mamba 前缀缓存在 ``align`` 模式下被标记为实验性。"

#: ../../source/mp/hybrid_models.rst:217
msgid ""
"See the :doc:`Qwen3.5 / Qwen3.6 recipe <../recipes/qwen3_5>` for the "
"validated end-to-end commands and the per-model block sizes."
msgstr ""
"请参阅 :doc:`Qwen3.5 / Qwen3.6 配方 <../recipes/qwen3_5>` "
"以获取经过验证的端到端命令和每个模型的块大小。"

